Ganguly 50 in 88 mins, off 59 balls, 6 fours
Ganguly/Dravid 2nd wicket partnership 87 runs, 81 mins, 109 balls
Ijaz Ahmed 50 in 95 mins, off 70 balls, 3x4
Azhar Mahmood 50 in 38 mins, off 34 balls, 6x4, 1x6
Abdur Razzaq/Azhar Mahmood 7th wicket partnership 72 runs, 54 mins, 61 balls
